    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal use, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. All major systems are functioning as intended, making this a dependable choice for its next owner.",
