    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some clear coat peeling on the hood, and a small dent on the rear quarter panel. Inside, the cabin shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets, though the heat and basic electronics remain operational. While the car starts and drives reliably, it will soon require new tires and a routine brake service. It is a dependable workhorse that reflects its mileage, offered at a price that leaves room for the next owner to perform necessary touch-ups.",
      "price": 18500.0,
