    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence. Meticulously maintained and preserved, it retains its original showroom luster both mechanically and aesthetically. Every surface\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior upholstery\u2014reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 43900.0,
